We partnered with the Surfrider Foundation to help share their story alongside this ocean inspired towel capsule. For each towel sold, a portion of proceeds will be donated to the Surfrider Foundation, a nonprofit who is dedicated to the protection  of the world's ocean, beaches, and marine conservation. Together we CAN make a difference. 🙏

Tag a friend to help share this message. 🌞🌊
